; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/gh-org.md

% gh-org, common

# List organizations for the authenticated user
gh org <_ls_list_>

# List a certain amount of organizations (defaults to 30)
gh org <_ls_list_> <__L___limit_> <100>

# Display help
gh org --help
